{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3c792069f0","title":"张春桥对上海体育界的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5f7723bdf6","index":0,"year":1967,"month":0,"day":0,"articleId":"3c792069f0","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"贺龙","id":"d0a2337495","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"fae13ac6b9","name":"张春桥"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"bd7418c514","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"来源：1967年11月3日清华大学井冈山斗批改战团编印《学习资料》第32期。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cd95afb6e6","type":"title","text":"张春桥对上海体育界的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"17db2ccf67","type":"paragraph","text":"上海市体革会胡永年同志问张春桥同志，体育界怎么办，专业以后要不要。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"217ba44444","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥同志讲：我们没有什么决定（中央文革），但是也谈过。专业队总还是要有，但是是否这样存在，不能象贺龙那样，在战争那样紧张情况下还带一个篮球队和一个剧团，我们专业队如何与工农兵结合，但总要有些高标准出来，问题是怎样与工农兵相结合。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aee277e315","type":"paragraph","text":"胡：是否保证重点项目存在，如足、篮、排……","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6f5e0342f","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥：不但要保持这几种项目存在，国际比赛总还是要有，我们可以象京剧那样搞样板，推陈出新，问题是怎样推陈出新，如何为工农兵服务。我们不要一概否定，我们要按毛主席的教导：“发展体育运动，增强人民体质。”为工农兵服务，为社会主义建设服务。……","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4dfc7dad9f","type":"paragraph","text":"胡：中央是否对体育界有最新指示？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"225ebd5848","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥：你最有发言权，斗批改不能靠我们，斗批改要靠你们，请你拿出一个方案来，我都是没学问的，最有学问的是毛主席。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"049a4ac98a","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：1967年11月3日清华大学井冈山斗批改战团编印《学习资料》第32期。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3c792069f0","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}